{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The woman came to me and said, Janko, quickly, quickly get dressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because during the day, I was in a shirt or very primitively dressed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't go out, it was winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, get quickly dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, what Germans?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I don't know, but the German SS is here with cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, they said they will-- I looked out from the window and I saw that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, but they have drums?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, yes, they have got kerosene.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they find here partisans, they will burn the village down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they-- don't worry, we have no partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were not guilty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because many of these villages were on the side of-- and this, luckily, was one of the villages-- they didn't have a Jew for 80 years in that village.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very proud of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this danger was not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for me, it was a danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew that if Germans come and occupy a small town or big one, they start to verify each one who lives there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And really, the next day, there was a drummer going in the small village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody from the village, including children and old people, must come to the head man's village-- house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there were, I don't know, 40 or 50 people, all together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to line up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To myself, I said, now, this is it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "John, now you are finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because verification had to take my false papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- we were standing in queue, one by one was let in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were sitting two SS men behind the table, the head man of the village, who was like a trustee.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each person who came in, he said, oh, yes, that's Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
